original_prompt: A modern turquoise car is prominently positioned in the center of the photo, capturing its front side in sharp focus. The car gleams under the afternoon sun, revealing its sleek design. Inside, there's a male driver with short-cropped hair and a female passenger with a ponytail, both attentively looking ahead. Behind the car, the blurred cityscape provides a beautiful bokeh effect, hinting at tall buildings and bustling streets. Several people of diverse descent and gender move about in the background, adding life to the urban scene.
